title: X-Men The Animated Series S02 (FOR PLEX)
description:
X-Men The Animated Series Season 2! Optimized for Plex!

These are the same files that DeliXiosO uploaded, and he should get all the credit for uploading such great content. I have only changed their name and their order so that they play nicer with Plex. 

If you use Plex with the DVD bundle plugin for organizing T.V. shows, then this is the version of this series that you want!

I hope you all enjoy!
